SUMMARY:BSO February Weekender
DESCRIPTION:THIS IS WHAT YOUVE BEEN WAITING FOR: \n🚀 BSO INFINITY EXPERIENCE WEEKENDER🚀\nFebruary 26 – March 1\, 2026 \n⚠️ ONLY 10 EARLY BIRD PASSES\nOnce these 10 passes are gone\, the price jumps. This is the lowest price you will see for our event! \n🔥 NEW ARTISTS\nWe are so excited to announce our amazing line up of world-class dancers to bring you an unforgettable experience:\n✨Monika & Victor from Tokyo 🇯🇵\n✨Luis & Tay from NYC mm\n✨Sagar & Amber from Indiana\n✨Brandon & Camila from Miami\n✨Yair & Lana i from Miami/Orlando\n✨Robinson & Larissa from Miami/Orlando \nSO family\n⭐AyJ\n⭐Josiah\n⭐Christian Hines\n⭐Tatiana\n⭐️Fabiola Santos\n⭐️Ariana \n🎧 The hottest DJs playing th hottest Bachata:\n👨‍🚀 DJ MoodShift\n🧑‍🚀 DJ 3DSommer
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/bso-february-weekender/
