SUMMARY:Latin Dance Class & Salsa Party on the Tampa Riverwalk!
DESCRIPTION:A Latin Dance Class for $1 or Donation! \n$1 Pop-up social at MacDill Park on the Tampa Riverwalk next to Hotel Tampa Riverwalk! \n\n\n\nA Latin Dance Class and Pop-up social at MacDill Park in The Tampa Riverwalk next to Hotel Tampa Riverwalk. \n  \nRELPro Dance will be bringing a local school to teach a class at the beginning of the event! \n  \nEvery month we dance under the lights with perfect views of the water on the Tampa Riverwalk! \n  \nHosted by RELPro Dance Promotions \n  \nPlease make music requests! $5-$10 Donations gladly accepted.
