SUMMARY:SALSA SATURDAY NIGHT DANCE
DESCRIPTION:Sat. Feb 28\, 2026\nDoors open at 7:00 pm.\nSalsa & Bachata lesson 7-8pm. \nSocial dance 8-10:00pm. Music by DJEzDoeSiT \nThe One-and-ONLY LATIN DANCE in Collegeville! \n⭐️ $15 at the Door \n⏰ 7:00 Salsa & Bachata Lesson! • 8:00 to 10:00 pm >> Dance..! \n==> The REAL Address is:\n222 E. Main Street\nCollegeville\, PA 19426 \n==================================== \n❤️ Hey! *** A NEW LATIN DANCE EVENT !! *** \n🗓 ⇨ ON Saturday\, Feb.28th. in Collegeville\, PA \n==================================== \nThe DEETS: \n👉 $15 \n😃 Beginner-Friendly! \n⇨ FREE Salsa & Bachata Lesson at 7:00 (included with the Admission Fee). \n🎉 Dress UP for a FUN Dance! Wear dance shoes if you have them. \n❤️ Bring your friends and get ready to dance! \n🕺🏻You’ll be stunned by the ballroom with the beautiful floor\, free (and safe) parking\, great music\, great people\, and more..! \nSee you there..!
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/salsa-saturday-night-dance/
