SUMMARY:SALSATECA FIESTA!
DESCRIPTION:SALSATECA FIESTA! SALSA & BACHATA SPECIAL PARTY\nOur regular Saturdays become a party on the last Saturday of every month. Experience an unforgettable Salsa & Bachata Party at the Zhulin Hidden Village in Lewisham.\nWe kick off the night with Salsa & Bachata lessons. If you’re new to dancing\, we recommend joining our beginners’ group. All levels are welcome! No prior experience or dance partner is needed. Many attendees come solo\, and we rotate partners throughout the lesson\, giving you the chance to dance with different people. If you’d prefer to stay with your own partner for the entire class\, just let the teacher know\, and we’ll be happy to accommodate you.\nClass Schedule:\n– 🕕 7:00 PM – 8:00 PM: Salsa (Cross Body) – All Levels\n– 🕖 8:00 PM – 9:00 PM: Bachata – All Levels\n– 🕗 9:00 PM – 01:00 AM: Party\nSince most Latin parties feature both Salsa and Bachata\, knowing both styles is both fun and practical!\nTeaching Lineup:\nSalsa:\n– Intermediate: Gabriel\n– Improvers: Femeto\n– Beginners: Virginia\nBachata:\n– Intermediate: Gabriel\n– Improvers: Femeto\n– Beginners: Virginia\nDJ Lineup: Gabriel ‘Happy Feet’\nGet ready to dance the night away as our amazing Dj Gabriel ‘ Happy Feet’ brings you the best of Salsa and Bachata music\, keeping the party going well into the night\n📍Venue:\nZhulin Hidden Village\n100-104 Lewisham High Street\nLondon\, SE13 5JH\nFind the venue 5 min walk from Lewisham station at the High Street by the clock tower\, above the British Heart Foundation.\nGet to Lewisham from London Bridge! Trains run every 5 minutes and take only 8 min to get to Lewisham!\nIf you’re searching for a Salsa club in London\, Bromley\, or Orpington\, this is the perfect party for you!\nCome dance\, learn\, and enjoy the lively atmosphere at Salsateca Fiesta!
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/salsateca-fiesta-2-2/2026-02-28/
LOCATION:WCKUK Lewisham\, Zhulin Hidden Village\, 100-104 Lewisham High Street\, London\, United Kingdom
CATEGORIES:London
END:VEVENT
