SUMMARY:Salsa Saturdays at Tailgaters Sports Bar and Grill
DESCRIPTION:Come join us for a fun salsa class every Saturday at 8pm at Tailgaters Sports Bar and Grill in Antioch!\n\n\nSign up at www.BayAreaSalsa.com for VIP or Table Reservations \nSalsa by the Bay \nWelcome to **La Zona Saturdays Beginners Salsa Class** at Tailgaters Sports Bar and Grll! \nJoin us on for a fun and energetic salsa dancing class. \nThe event starts with check-in at **7:30pm**\, followed by the class at **8:00pm**. \nFollowing the Class\, participants 21+ are Welcome to stay for the weekly Salsa by the Bay Event \n$15-$20 at the Door. \nNo experience is necessary – our friendly instructors will guide you through the basics of salsa dancing. Whether you’re looking to learn a new skill\, meet new people\, or just have a good time\, this class is perfect for beginners. Don’t miss out on the opportunity to spice up your Sundays with some salsa dancing! Great for Singles\, Couples and Groups! No Partner Required! \nTailgaters is the best place to party with friends and family! Plan your next birthday celebration with us! With plentiful FREE secure parking! It will be an event you will soon not forget! None of your friends will want to miss it! \nSalsa by the Bay is the best setting for special events\, get togethers\, celebrations or a date night. \nSpace is limited so don’t wait any longer\, book now and let’s salsa! \n21+ after 9pm
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/salsa-class-antioch-saturdays-8pm-tailgaters-sports-bar-and-grill/2026-02-28/
LOCATION:Tailgaters Sports Bar & Grill\, 4605 Golf Course Road\, Antioch\, CA 94531\, Antioch\, CA\, 94531\, US
CATEGORIES:San Francisco
END:VEVENT
