SUMMARY:Bachata ConeXion Saturdays 'Azure Nights
DESCRIPTION:🎉 Bachateros of Melbourne City — Get Excited! 🎉\n.\n💫 Azure Nights has arrived! Step into a world of blue\, white\, and pure bachata vibes for a night of dance\, music\, and connection! 💃🕺\n.\n📅 Date: Saturday\, 28th of February\n.\n🕗 Time:\n8:00 pm — Bachata Workshop (Open Level)\n9:00 pm – 1:00 am — Social Dancing\n.\n📍 Location:\nSokol Melbourne Inc\n497 Queensberry Street\, North Melbourne\n.\n🎶 Music Policy:\n70% Bachata • 30% Salsa • + Touch of Kizomba & Zouk\n.\n👔 Dress Code:\nBlue & White — dress to impress ✨\n.\n🎧 DJ Lineup:\nDJ Hong Starr\, DJ JT (from Spain)\, DJ Spanky\n.\n🎟️ Booking Link to Save:\nhttps://www.trybooking.com/DJAVW\n.\n💃🕺 Walk-in Prices:\n8:00 pm Workshop + Social — $22\n9:00 pm Social Only — $18\nAfter 11:30 pm — $13\n.\n💻 Online Prices (Save $$):\n8:00 pm Workshop + Social — $18\n9:00 pm till 1:00 am Social — $14\n.\n🎫 Limited Tickets Online — Book Now & Save!\nhttps://www.trybooking.com/DIMBD\n.\n📲 Stay Updated: Click “Going” on the event!\n.\n🌟 Join the Bachata ConeXion Family and experience that ConeXion feeling!\n.\n🌍 Connecting the Bachata Community of Melbourne!\n.\n🎉 Everyone Welcome! Beginners\, experienced dancers\, first-timers — we got you!\n.\n📸 Instagram: @bachataconexion\n✉ Become a Member: bachataconexion18@gmail.com\n(FREE to join)\n.\n⚠ Friendly Reminder:\nBy attending you acknowledge:\n✔ You are fit to participate\n✔ Refund/credit available for cancellations (online bookings only)\n✔ Organisers/instructors are not liable for injuries\n✔ Photos & videos may be taken for marketing/social use\n.\n💙 Let’s light up the dance floor in Blue & White and make it a night to remember! 💙✨
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/bachata-conexion-saturdays-azure-nights/
LOCATION:497-499 Queensberry St\, 497-499 Queensberry St\, North Melbourne\, VIC\, 3053\, Australia
CATEGORIES:Melbourne
END:VEVENT
